memberdef.name: create

detaileddescription.para: creates and returns a new basic layer named <name>, of type <material> for the given technology (some geometrical characteristics can also be specified).

simplesect.title: Caution: Throws an exception if the technology is null, if the name is
simplesect.para: empty, if a layer of same name already exists or if we overflow the capacity of the bit field associated to the layer mask.

The extract number is a kind of logic number. In example the CP layer which represent a poly layer should have the same extract number as the CPG layer which represent a poly layer used to realize the transistor gates. While extractions process, layers which have the same extract number are considered as equivalents. A null value indicates that the extraction should ignore this layer.
